"title": "5256: city",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5256",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A large walled centre of population providing security for its inhabitants. The OT often uses the term as a symbol of the security of heaven.</p>\n<h2>Types of city</h2>\n<h3>Ancient cities</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:17\">GEN 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen10:10-Gen10:12\">GEN 10:10–10:12</a></p>\n<h3>Fortified cities</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:34-Num32:36\">NUM 32:34–32:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:1\">DEU 9:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:20\">JOS 10:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh14:12\">JOS 14:12</a></p>\n<h3>Royal cities</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:2\">JOS 10:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam27:5\">1SA 27:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:7\">1CH 11:7</a></p>\n<h3>Cities of refuge</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:41-Deut4:43\">DEU 4:41–4:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:1-Deut19:13\">DEU 19:1–19:13</a></p>\n<h2>Cities were frequently large</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:28\">DEU 1:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:2-Jonah3:3\">JON 3:2–3:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:10\">DEU 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:1\">DEU 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:4\">NEH 7:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:11\">JON 4:11</a></p>\n<h2>Cities were surrounded by walls</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:5\">DEU 3:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:12\">EZR 4:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:32-2Cor11:33\">2CO 11:32–11:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:52\">DEU 28:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:15\">JOS 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:1\">1KI 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:13\">1KI 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:14\">2CH 33:14</a></p>\n<h2>Cities were places of security</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:17\">NUM 32:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:20\">JOS 10:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr11:5-2Chr11:12\">2CH 11:5–11:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:6\">2CH 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:2\">2CH 17:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:5\">JER 4:5</a></p>\n<h2>Cities could fall</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:7\">2SA 5:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:3\">NEH 1:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:58\">JER 51:58</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut20:12\">DEU 20:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut20:19-Deut20:20\">DEU 20:19–20:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:17-1Kgs16:18\">1KI 16:17–16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:1-2Kgs25:4\">2KI 25:1–25:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:19\">ISA 13:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:24-Jer32:25\">JER 32:24–32:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:9\">AMO 5:9</a></p>\n<h2>The holy city</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:1-Ps48:2\">PSA 48:1–48:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:36\">1KI 11:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:21\">1KI 14:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:7\">1CH 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh11:1\">NEH 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:1\">ISA 52:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:29\">JER 25:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:16\">DAN 9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:35\">MAT 5:35</a></p>\n<h2>City law</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:29-Lev25:30\">LEV 25:29–25:30</a></p>\n<h2>The city as a symbol</h2>\n<h3>Of strength</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:18\">JER 1:18</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Of heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:10\">HEB 11:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:16\">HEB 11:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:22\">HEB 12:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:14\">HEB 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2\">REV 21:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:20-Rev21:27\">REV 21:20–21:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:1-Rev22:5\">REV 22:1–22:5</a></p>",
